- 'Classes of the grand voyage' refers to the different passenger classes (1, 2, 3) on the ship;
- 'Paid more than the average fare' means the average fare for the class is higher than the overall average fare of all passengers.

- 'Classes of passengers' refers to the different passenger classes (1, 2, 3) on the ship;
