- "grandeur of the cabins" refers to the total capacity of the cabin.

- 'Adult Male' refers to males older than 20 years; 'Young Male' refers to males 20 years or younger;
- 'Adult Female' refers to females older than 20 years; 'Young Female' refers to females 20 years or younger;
- 'has_family' indicates whether a passenger has any family members (parents/children or siblings/spouses) aboard the ship;
